rComments: Professor Richer is highly approachable, really helpful and a positive person overall. He was my prof for SOC211 and his way of lecturing was really effective in a positive manner. He answers questions to the point so that you understand them properly. Also, he is my research advisor and really helpful in that respect as well.

Professor Richer is a really good prof and you can tell he is knowledgable on his work. He encourages class deliberation, so it really does not feel like a lecture. He actually makes the effort to reach out to students and make sure they're grasping his work. The class is very participation intensive.. if you dont go you will not pass.
